    {
      "title": "Instructions\nTask\nPlease amend the following response based on the Query, Response, and Reference Text\nIn this task, you are required to amend a short response to a user's query for conversational\nnaturalness, and introduce a follow-up question. A follow-up question consists of an enquiry\nspecified below\nregarding any additional information which could be useful/of interest to the user.\nQuery: ${query}\nFor the amended response, please ensure that:\nResponse: ${response}\n\n    The amended response in conversationally natural and cordial. DO NOT simply restate\n\nReference Text: ${supp_info}\nFor the follow-up question, please ensure that:\nType amended response here\n\u2022 The follow-up question enquires if the user would like a specific piece on information.\nDO NOT include generic follow-up questions such as 'Would you like to learn more\nabout the film?' or 'Is there anything you would like to know about this building?'.\nType Follow-up Question here\n\n    The information referred to in the follow-up question can be found in the Reference\n\n\u00b7 The follow-up question does not request information from the user. Eq. 'What is the\nheight of the Empire State building?",
